<eugippius.excerpta_ex_operibus_augustini urn:cts:latinLit:stoa0119.stoa003.opp-lat1.340>	Moses exaltauit serpentem in heremo. CCCXVIII. 343. Resurrectioni futurae utrum Lazari an Christi resurrectio congruat.
